    <item>
      <title>苹果公司最新人力资源变动：首席招聘人员转投 Citadel</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/citadel-hires-apple-s-top-recruiting-executive-as-new-people-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 首席招聘主管将离职，出任投资公司 Citadel 的首席人才官，这标志着这家 iPhone 制造商动荡的人力资源团队又有一名重要人物离职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/citadel-hires-apple-s-top-recruiting-executive-as-new-people-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 17:51:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国最繁忙贸易枢纽第三季度货运量突破疫情期间纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/busiest-us-trade-hub-beat-pandemic-cargo-record-in-third-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于企业在可能的关税上调之前继续运送货物，并试图避开飓风和备用港口的劳工中断，美国最繁忙的集装箱码头在上个季度创下了疫情期间创下的纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/busiest-us-trade-hub-beat-pandemic-cargo-record-in-third-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 17:30:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行盈利强劲，推动股市突破 2023 年水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/banks-put-up-strong-earnings-pushing-stocks-beyond-2023-levels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是一个漫长而艰难的攀登，但好于预期的财报季正在推动银行股回到 2023 年区域银行业危机之前的最高水平，表明投资者终于恢复了对金融业的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/banks-put-up-strong-earnings-pushing-stocks-beyond-2023-levels</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 16:06:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
